{\raggedright\large \textbf{MATE Robotics Competition, Technical Lead}\\
{Willamette University}\\[5pt]}
\normalsize{I was the technical lead for a robotics team. I lead the design of a robot whose goal was to perform tasks underwater. Tasks I accomplished:}\\
\hspace*{0.2in}-Designed the electrical system using several different microcontrollers and control boards, which allowed our robot to receive control signals from an above-water computer\\
